configure.args      --prefix=${prefix}

long_description \
The fuzz generator is designed to attack certain kinds \
of software and expose one particular kind of bug common in software. \
This is the situation where the programmer implicity makes some assumtions \
about the data stream that the program will be parsing. If the data stream \
is substantially different then the program might not be able to deal with it.  
